graph TD
    User[User] -->|HTTP Request| API[FastAPI Layer]
    API -->|Start Workflow| TemporalClient[Temporal Client]
    TemporalClient -->|Trigger| Orchestrator[Orchestration Workflow]
    
    subgraph Temporal Cluster
        Orchestrator -->|Activity: Classify| Classifier[Classification Activity]
        
        Orchestrator -->|Decision: KB| KBFlow[KB Sub-Workflow]
        Orchestrator -->|Decision: Action| ActionFlow[Action Sub-Workflow]
        
        KBFlow -->|Activity: RAG| KBAgent[LangGraph KB Agent]
        ActionFlow -->|Activity: Plan/Execute| ActionAgent[LangGraph Action Agent]
        
        ActionFlow -->|Signal: Human Approval| HumanLoop[Human Approval]
        
        ActionAgent -->|External Call| ExternalAPI[External APIs]
    end
    
    Orchestrator -->|Consolidate| Response[Final Response]
    Response -->|Return| API
    
    subgraph Persistence
        PG[(PostgreSQL\nTemporal State)]
        Redis[(Redis\nLangGraph Checkpoint)]
    end
    
    subgraph Observability
        Arize[Arize AI / Phoenix]
    end
    
    Orchestrator -.->|Workflow History| PG
    KBAgent -.->|Thread State| Redis
    ActionAgent -.->|Thread State| Redis
    
    KBAgent -.->|Traces| Arize
    ActionAgent -.->|Traces| Arize
